    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear or aging. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously cared for to maintain its like-new status. This is an exceptional example for a buyer who demands the highest level of quality and performance.",
