      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute, this represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine example of the marque.",
