    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly flawless condition\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is! I'm happy to answer any questions or hop on a call to chat more about it. Can't wait to find this gem a great new home! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
